+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${PKGSTEM} on OpenBSD
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Fonts
=====

${PKGSTEM} needs a Nerd Font installed and enabled in your terminal.
See `fonts/nerd-fonts` packages to install one.

Shell Integration
=================

shells/zsh
----------

To enable ${PKGSTEM}, add this to the end of your ~/.zshrc:

```
eval "$(starship init zsh)"
```

shells/bash
-----------

To enable ${PKGSTEM}, add this to the end of your ~/.bashrc:

```
eval "$(starship init bash)"
```

shells/fish
-----------

To enable ${PKGSTEM}, add this to the end of your ~/.config/fish/config.fish:

```
starship init fish | source
```

